text: Abdul Haseeb Khan (Urdu: عبدل حسیب خان) is a Pakistani Politician and a Member of Senate of Pakistan. ==Political career== In March 2009 he was elected to the Senate of Pakistan on general seat as MQM candidate. He is member of Senate committee of National Health Services, Regulations and Coordination, Information Technology and Telecommunication Commerce and Textile Industry, Industries and Production and Employees Welfare Fund. ==See also== * List of Senators of Pakistan * Ayatullah Durrani * Hafiz Hamdullah ==References== Category:Living people Category:Muhajir people Category:Members of the Senate of Pakistan Category:Muttahida Qaumi Movement politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
